Shows service bulletins. Note that CTA has a system-wide bulletin about the Wacker Drive reconstruction, and both MTA and TRIPS have system wide bulletins. Also added icons from Dmitriy Vysotskiy, replacing the main icon and allowing a choice of colors when creating a shortcut.
